<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA73">
<l>karuttiṉā ṉīkarutiṟ ṟellā muṭaṉē</l>
<l>tiruttalāñ cikkeṉa nāṉcoṉṉēṉ - paruttaraṅka</l>
<l>veḷḷanī rēṟṟā ṉaṭikkamala nīvirumpi</l>
<l>yuḷḷamē yeppōtu mōtu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be perfecting together all you intended with</l>
<l>[your] intention. I have told [you] firmly. Recite all the time,</l> 
<l>mind, desiring the feet lotuses of him who receives</l>
<l>the flooding water with huge waves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
